reviewText: I bought this DVD for my 2 year old  grandson who loves music and dancing. It has lots of both. Great quality and quick shipping.
my six year old son loves this video. you can't go wrong with any of the jim henson children's videos.
Great dvd, recommend to anyone with chldren of any age, gets them moving.  Item was as described, packaging great.  Loved it
I took the "shake a leg" dvd out from the library and my daughter just had an absolute blast.  She is just about 2 1/2 years old and she dances during the entire DVD.  This is a definite buy!!!
